'''[[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] spark [[Grenade/Legends|grenades]]''' were an improvised explosive that caused the conductors in [[Droid/Legends|droids]] and other technological devices to short circuit. In [[15 ABY/Legends|15 ABY]], [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] created one out of a power source and a twisted-pair det to fry [[Cronal|Perek's]] [[Technobeast|technobeasts]].  

